Name: brachial plexus neoplasm
Definition: An anxiety disorder where fear and anxiety are triggered by a specific stimulus or situation.

Name: lumbar plexus neoplasm
Definition: A cervical adenosquamous carcinoma that is a rare form and is composed of cells with a glass-like cytoplasm.
